{"code":0,"data":[{"cid":23505,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":3913,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"冠姓权又可以来吵一波了","timestamp":1592893643,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":23508,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":3913,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"这不就是结构性压迫吗？","timestamp":1592893649,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":23520,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":3913,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"所以呢？","timestamp":1592893678,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":23524,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":3913,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"跟妈妈姓跟爸爸姓的对半不就没人问了？","timestamp":1592893703,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":23552,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":3913,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Carol: 这是孩子跟你姓能解决的问题吗？","timestamp":1592893799,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":23557,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":3913,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"我个人觉得，确实是存在着结构性压迫的，但是我觉得这件事本身的压迫意义并不是很大，孩子的姓氏并不能代表父亲母亲的地位高低。\n如果说要争取平权，还是有很多地方可以去争取的。","timestamp":1592893818,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":23617,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":3913,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"今日割五城，明日割十城，然后得一夕安寝？要平权就是革命，而革命不是请客吃饭。结构性压迫的破除就是以忍受不方便的方式去扭转不方便为方便，我觉得这种争取的尝试是有意义的。","timestamp":1592894097,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":83282,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Eve","permissions":["report"],"pid":3913,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re : 实话，现在并没有人care你孩子的名字，因为大家都很忙，如果你孩子上了T大，可能还有点关注","timestamp":1593853950,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":83289,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Eve","permissions":["report"],"pid":3913,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Alice: 有什么好吵的？互相尊重，妻子生孩子流那么多血那么痛，如果主动要求姓氏并不过分，为这种小事吵架我觉得这段婚姻可以考虑结束了，男方太自私自利","timestamp":1593854071,"type":"text","url":""}],"post":{"attention":false,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"likenum":4,"permissions":["report","fold"],"pid":3913,"reply":9,"tag":null,"text":"突然看到了冠名\n记得之前见过这样一段话：\n我并不反对孩子随母亲姓，以后带着孩子出去，所有人都得问母亲一句：“为什么孩子跟你姓？因为离婚了吗？”然后问我一句：“为什么孩子要跟女方姓？因为是前夫的孩子吗？”我就会一本正经地告诉大家：“因为我尊重女权。”每问一次，我都要回答一次\n是尊重女权吗？是\n有必要吗？没必要\n","timestamp":1592893560,"type":"text","updated_at":1606782585,"url":"","vote":{}}}